{"TopicId":200681,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Mac user in troube with cycle through spaceships","CreatedByName":"Dukie76","CreatedById":210363,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-27T16:32:34Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dukie76","CreatedById":210363,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-27T16:32:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi Guys, my first post and I hope my question is not too stupid (didn\u0027t find the answer\u00A0with the search).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m on my first rescue mission and I want to cycle through the two space ships, but nothing works. I\u0027ve tried a lot of combinations like \u0022alt\u002B(\u0022 or the German \u00DF which is in some manuals). Also every single F-Key and \u002B\u00A0with option and without ... I\u0027ve found also \u0022shift\u002Balt\u002B(\u0022, but this only starts the engine \u003Cspan\u003E:-(\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPretty desperate now because I LOVE the game. Can anybody help me with this please?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wobbly Av8r","CreatedById":206697,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-27T17:04:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry the \u0022[\u0022 or \u0022]\u0022 (bracket) keys? That\u0027s what works on Windows...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bej Kerman","CreatedById":182413,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-27T17:07:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223933152\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221614445465\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022206697\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Wobbly Av8r\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Wobbly Av8r said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTry the \u0022[\u0022 or \u0022]\u0022 (bracket) keys? That\u0027s what works on Windows...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas just about to say, you don\u0027t use key combos when switching vessels...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-27T18:02:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about going to the settings and remapping the commands to something you like?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-27T18:16:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223933197\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221614448920\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about going to the settings and remapping the commands to something you like?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just like to mention that, back when I\u00A0was a new player,\u00A0took me\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eweek\u003C/em\u003Es to realize that option\u00A0was in the main menu and not\u00A0the in game\u00A0menu.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Curveball Anders","CreatedById":107529,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-28T09:52:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223933197\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022200681\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221614448920\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow about going to the settings and remapping the commands to something you like?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is extra important if you\u0027re using a non uk/us keyboard.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}